Author: Oracle COMPONENT NAME: LKM JMS XML to SQL Component Version: 10.1.3.2 Compatibility: ODI 10.1.3.5.0 and above
DESCRIPTION Loading Knowledge Module Loads XML data from a JMS compliant Message Oriented Middleware (MOM) to any ISO-92 compliant target database. This module uses Sunopsis Agent to read selected XML data from the source MOM and write the result in the target temporary table created dynamically.
REQUIREMENTS The SYNCHRO_JMS_TO_XML option must be set to YES in the first interface loading the message to the XML schema. In order to ensure that the message is successfully recieved AND propagated, the JMS_COMMIT option must be set to NO for all interfaces except the last one.
OPTIONS (Refer to Option descriptions for more information on each option)
LIMITATIONS

Load the JMS messages to XML
This option should be set to YES for the first interface accessing the message. In subsequent interfaces which access the same message, it should be set to NO.
